      • tryListFiles

        org.json.simple.JSONObject tryListFiles(java.lang.String uid,
                                      java.lang.String serverName,
                                      int port,
                                      java.lang.String path,
                                      FileManager fileManager)
        Tries to list files. Returns an "authentication" response if the user is not authorized. The authentication response contains a URL to redirect to either Google or Dropbox to authenticate. // uid is in the query string, Query string takes precendence. Treat it as a new login.
